description: Easy-to-use generic Kotlin API client for connecting to various AI providers with multiplatform support. Supported AI providers: AI21 Lab, Anthropic, AWS Bedrock, Azure OpenAI, Cerebras, Cohere, DeepSeek, Google Gemini, Grok, Inception Labs, Mistral, Novita, OpenAI, SambaNova, Together AI, Yandex AI Studio.
